item.title: Partyhat > Cracker
item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

The Christmas Cracker & Blue Partyhat are still worth more than max cash street price, so they are rarely traded through the Grand Exchange, which is why their market price isn’t rising as much as the others since it only takes into account items which are bought/sold through the GE.

Also gold isn’t as hard to come by as it was a few years ago, so it somewhat evens out a bit.
